    "en": {
      "title": "Dickwella Estate achieves record for FBOPF1 grade",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the Uva Medium, Dickwella Estate, Hali Ella, continues its record-breaking run in 2022.",
        "An invoice of Dickwella FBOPF1 achieves a record of Rs. 2,650 per kg at the Colombo Tea Auction on 16 and 17 August. The previous record for this grade was Rs. 2,550 per kg.",
        "Dickwella Estate belongs to Malwatte Valley Plantations PLC. This Estate is managed by Regional Manager Chaminda Perera and the factory is under the supervision of Master Tea Maker A.M. Shajahan",
        "This tea was purchased by Inter Tea Ltd. and successfully marketed by Asia Siyaka Commodities PLC."
      ],
